abstracts.cdata!:
The project's major objectives are:
            (a) to raise agricultural production, incomes, and
            employment levels in Erzurum province; and (b) to improve
            conditions of rural life. These objectives will be achieved
            by: (i) establishment of an intensive multi-disciplinary
            extension service; (ii) development and demonstration of
            technical packages for cereals and forage crops, including
            improved pasture and range management practices; (iii)
            extension of irrigation facilities and soil conservation;
            (iv) provision of credit for production and investment,
            including beekeeping operations, 3 honeypackaging and
            marketing units, improvement of 3 existing milk collection
            centers and establishment of 7 new ones.
